<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>حَمَّاد وكناه.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٣٨٣٨ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو شَيبَان:</span> أَشْرَس.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">عَن:</span> الْحسن، قَالَه البُخَارِيّ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٣٨٣٩ - أَبُو شَيبَان.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> سعيد الْجريرِي <span class="c2">(ق ١٦١ / ب)</span> .<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> عبد الرَّزَّاق، وَيحيى بن آدم.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٣٨٤٠ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو شَيبَان:</span> سَأَلَهُ حَمَّاد بن زيد،<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>عَن حَدِيث سُلَيْمَان بن أبي دَاوُد.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>أرَاهُ الأول، قَالَه ابْن مَنْدَه.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>٣٨٤١ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو شَجَرَة:</span> يزِيد بن شَجَرَة.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>ذكر فِي الصَّحَابَة، وَلَا يثبت وَهُوَ من تَابِعِيّ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>أهل الشَّام.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>٣٨٤٢ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو شَجَرَة:</span> وَقيل: أَبُو الْقَاسِم:<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>كثير بن مرّة.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> خَالِد بن معدان، وَأَبُو الزَّاهِرِيَّة<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وكناه.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>٣٨٤٣ - أَبُو شرَاحِيل،<span class="c5"> وَقيل:</span> أَبُو شراحبيل:<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>تقدم ذكره.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>٣٨٤٤ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو شريك:</span> معقل بن مَالك.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> عقبَة الْأَصَم.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> البُخَارِيّ وكناه.<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>٣٨٤٥ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو شريك:</span> يحيى بن يزِيد بن<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>حَمَّاد الْمصْرِيّ.<a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> رشدين بن سعد وَغَيره.<a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span><span class="c2">(وَمن أَفْرَاد الصَّحَابَة)</span><a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p26"></span>٣٨٤٦ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو شقيرة:</span> لَهُ صُحْبَة.<a href="#p26" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p27"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> مخلد بن عقبَة.<a href="#p27" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p28"></span>٣٨٤٧ - أَبُو شهم.<a href="#p28" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p29"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> قيس بن أبي حَازِم.<a href="#p29" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p30"></span>٣٨٤٨ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو شاه:</span> لَهُ ذكر فِي حَدِيث أبي<a href="#p30" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p31"></span>هُرَيْرَة.<a href="#p31" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p32"></span>٣٨٤٩ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو الشموس:</span> البلوي، كنت مَعَ<a href="#p32" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p33"></span>النَّبِي صلى الله عَلَيْهِ وَسلم فِي غَزْوَة تَبُوك.<a href="#p33" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p34"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> مطير أَبُو سليم عَنهُ.<a href="#p34" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p35"></span>٣٨٥٠ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو شِرَاك:</span> عَمْرو بن عَمْرو الفِهري<a href="#p35" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p36"></span>شهد بَدْرًا مَعَ النَّبِي صلى الله عَلَيْهِ وَسلم.<a href="#p36" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p37"></span>قَالَه الْوَاقِدِيّ.<a href="#p37" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p38"></span><span class="c2">(وَمن التَّابِعين)</span><a href="#p38" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p39"></span>٣٨٥١ - أَبُو شقيرة.<a href="#p39" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p40"></span>رأى الْحسن، وَالْحُسَيْن رَضِي الله عَنْهُمَا.<a href="#p40" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p41"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> لَيْث بن أبي سليم.<a href="#p41" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p42"></span>٣٨٥٢ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو الشمَال:</span> ابْن ضباب.<a href="#p42" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p43"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> أبي أَيُّوب.<a href="#p43" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p44"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> مَكْحُول.<a href="#p44" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p45"></span>٣٨٥٣ - أَبُو شَرْقي.<a href="#p45" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p46"></span>عَن أبي عُثْمَان النَّهْدِيّ.<a href="#p46" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p47"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> شُعْبَة.<a href="#p47" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>